author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
My tour with The Darkness begins this week, so once again I'm away from my studio and in unfamiliar surroundings. Sebastian Murphy agreed to meet me there for a long form interview, which we'll bring you later this week. But ahead of that,  I wanted to check out Viagra Boys' latest release - Uno II. My very dear family friend, Danny Bolton joined me.

To watch Uno II without the pub chat: https://youtu.be/9kWgvEKIo4c?si=ir_5qvLGXE3TA_qX

The new Darkness album comes out on the 28th March,   you can pre-order 'Dreams On Toast' on CD, vinyl or cassette here: https://thedarkness.lnk.to/dreamsontoast/

See The Darkness on tour across the UK this month,  tickets are on sale here: https://www.thedarknesslive.com/tour-dates/

From mid March, watch more episodes of Justin Hawkins Rides Again and find Behind The Scenes footage from The Darkness On Tour on my Patreon: http://www.patreon.com/jushawk

For Cameo messages: https://www.cameo.com/justinhawkins
